== Deaths == * [[弘仁]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[811]] {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakagami Tamuramaro|ja|坂上田村麻呂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a shōgun (born [[758]]) <Note: Another source, "Otomo Yoshinobu," lists May 6.>
