== Deaths == * [[弘仁]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:811|811]] [[:en:June 17|June 17]]) – [[:en:Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|Sakagami Tamuramaro]], a shōgun (born [[:en:758|758]]) <Note: Another source, "Otomo Yoshinobu," lists May 6.>
